i'm given three things, want to return one.

FIND ALL PEOPLE WITH SECRET

there's people, each assigned a number.
some of them have meetings with each other.
i know who, and when.

i'm told, a person can attend several meetings at once.

there's a secret, whenever someone with the secret
has a meeting, they share it with who they're meeting with.

two people initially know the secret.

my job is to find everyone who knows the secret
after all meetings have taken place.

NOW, TO SOLVE.

well, pick the meetings as they happen.
if one person knows the secret,
they and every one they have a meeting with know too.

pick the next meeting.
i'd need a way to track who knows the secret.
a set would suffice.